> _Báo cáo chi tiết: xem artifact `evidence-sourcecode-verification.md`_

##### Kết Quả Xác Minh

| # | Claim | Status | Source Code Reference | Ghi chú |
|:--|:------|:-------|:---------------------|:--------|
| 1 | MySQL connector tương thích StarRocks | ✅ Verified | `packages/datasources/mysql/index.cjs` — dùng `mysql2`, thuần MySQL protocol | CTE count query có `.catch()` fallback |
| 2 | AI generate Evidence pages | ✅ Verified | `packages/lib/preprocess/src/extract-queries/extract-queries.cjs` — parse SQL from fenced code blocks | Query name phải match regex `/^[a-zA-Z_$][a-zA-Z0-9d_$]*$/` |
| 3 | File watcher auto-detect | ✅ Verified | `packages/evidence/cli.js` L51-101 — chokidar watch `./pages/**` | HMR triggered khi AI viết file mới |
| 4 | Query chaining | ✅ Verified | `extract-queries.cjs` L159-227 — `${query_name}` syntax | Max 15 chain depth, circular ref detection |
| 5 | Source → Parquet pipeline | ✅ Verified | `packages/lib/sdk/src/plugins/datasources/evalSources.js` → `buildMultipartParquet()` | Apache Arrow + ZSTD compression |
| 6 | Static build deployable | ✅ Verified | `cli.js` L411 — `npx serve build` | Compatible với Nginx reverse proxy |
| 7 | External query files | ✅ Verified | `extract-queries.cjs` L19-33 — read from `./queries/` directory | Frontmatter reference: `queries: [file.sql]` |

##### Điều Chỉnh Kỹ Thuật Sau Review

1. **Data Freshness**: Evidence **KHÔNG** live-query StarRocks. Pipeline là one-time snapshot qua `npm run sources` → Parquet files. AI Agent cần orchestrate refresh:
   ```python
   # Trigger incremental refresh
   subprocess.run(["npm", "run", "sources", "--", "--changed", "--sources", "starrocks_analytics"])
   ```

2. **StarRocks Special Types**: `BITMAP`, `HLL`, `ARRAY`, `MAP`, `STRUCT` sẽ fallback thành STRING trong Evidence type mapping. AI queries cần CAST:
   ```sql
   -- ❌ SELECT bitmap_col FROM table
   -- ✅ SELECT BITMAP_TO_STRING(bitmap_col) as bitmap_str FROM table
   ```

3. **Connection Config** (corrected):
   ```yaml
   # sources/starrocks_analytics/connection.yaml
   name: starrocks_analytics
   type: mysql
   options:
     host: ${EVIDENCE_SR_HOST}
     port: 9030
     database: analytics_db
     user: evidence_reader
     password: ${EVIDENCE_SR_PASSWORD}
   ```

4. **Source Query Best Practice**: Avoid `SELECT *` from large tables. Use pre-aggregated queries hoặc StarRocks Materialized Views:
   ```sql
   -- sources/starrocks_analytics/monthly_revenue.sql
   SELECT * FROM analytics_db.mv_daily_kpi_summary
   WHERE report_date >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 90 DAY)
   ```

5. **Parquet Size Warning**: Evidence logs warning khi Parquet file > 100MB (build-parquet.js L211). Với StarRocks data lớn, cần limit source queries.

